reviewText: I  for myself it was different for my 3yr old grandson because it was silent but quite a experience for him

ReelClassic DVD is  truly a grassroots company. Owned by former film collector Mark Roth, he distributes DVD's directly from film transfers. NOT video sources.  I purchased this great set a few years back, and I can honestly say it's the best transfers of any silent Felix shorts. The musical score is appropriate, with some shorts being scored by Ben Model.
